Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.11,0:00:15.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,曾經很懦弱的 Yesterday
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.75,0:00:19.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很想大哭一場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.12,0:00:22.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不可以氣餒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.69,0:00:25.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不論何時也不是孤獨一人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.39,0:00:30.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,遙遠的夢想在閃耀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.13,0:00:33.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,將它找回來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.70,0:00:38.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,把雙眼閉上便可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.67,0:00:43.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在心中的一個角落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.78,0:00:47.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就算留下傷痕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.88,0:00:55.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要害怕 現在是兩個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.64,0:01:00.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要放棄 Step by step
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.76,0:01:04.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,抓著夢想 Your Fight Jump
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.50,0:01:10.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,經常也和你一起向明天邁進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.77,0:01:14.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,繼續前進 Step by step
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:15.51,0:01:18.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想堅信著 Your Fight Jump
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.71,0:01:24.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想向著天空大聲呼叫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.22,0:01:27.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,燃燒著 in my heart
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.89,0:01:38.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我叫戰部渡.屹立在遙遠天空上的星界山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.02,0:01:43.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因為被多壞達支配了的關係\N令創界山變成了黑暗的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.43,0:01:47.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣下去又會再次變成被魔界支配的山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.78,0:01:53.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我再次成為了救世主\N與火美子、師傅和龍神丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.56,0:01:56.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一起為了打倒多壞達,以第七星界為目標出發了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.56,0:02:01.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今天也會是"超"有趣又有型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.68,0:02:12.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,第三話\N牆壁鎮的一半兄弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.30,0:02:24.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,竟在那裏有瀑布
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.59,0:02:28.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼?那不是個巨大的啤酒杯嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.16,0:02:32.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那麼說的話,這條河是啤酒河…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.18,0:02:37.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,說起來也差不多到了喝生啤的季節了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.52,0:02:40.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.94,0:02:43.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,師傅…師傅啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.39,0:02:45.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你在發什麼呆啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.18,0:02:47.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.87,0:02:51.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,倒是怎樣也好,我們去那邊看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.42,0:02:54.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對呢,對呢!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.98,0:02:58.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等一等!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.20,0:03:00.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼了?師傅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.59,0:03:01.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.80,0:03:14.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡,這裏也沒有花呢.真傷腦筋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.85,0:03:18.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,以前一定是個很美麗的花田呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.55,0:03:21.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因為星之風沒有吹起的關係呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.52,0:03:25.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,多壞達那家夥 真的不能饒恕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.85,0:03:31.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的呢,渡啊,無論怎樣也要打倒多壞達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.24,0:03:34.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯,加油吧!師傅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.34,0:03:34.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.87,0:03:36.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,剪刀!勝了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.59,0:03:41.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你們是布,是我勝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.20,0:03:43.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,火美子第一,火美子厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.78,0:04:07.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是個奇怪的鎮呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.59,0:04:11.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很香的氣味呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.89,0:04:15.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是從那間餐廳內傳出來的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.24,0:04:17.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我要吃朱古力芭菲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.86,0:04:22.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,火美子,沒事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.70,0:04:25.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在正中間有道牆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.14,0:04:30.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要你們久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.52,0:04:33.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不客氣了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.96,0:04:36.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是真是奇怪的杯呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.45,0:04:37.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這是豬排飯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.79,0:04:40.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,請,這是天婦羅烏東
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.36,0:04:44.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼了?全部只有一半啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.84,0:04:48.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而且你那樣子是怎麼回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.83,0:04:54.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是,其實這個喜傑喜傑鎮\N不論什麼也是分開一半的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.30,0:04:59.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是支配這市鎮的多壞達手下\N一半布其兄弟關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.91,0:05:01.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼?多壞達的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.10,0:05:11.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哥哥,果然一半這東西真好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.70,0:05:16.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,當然了,因為我們是一半布其兄弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.55,0:05:21.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是這個星界山,第一感情好的兄弟,弟弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.15,0:05:23.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以什麼也一人一半
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.26,0:05:25.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,市鎮、人、食物也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.33,0:05:28.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,全部也感情很好地一人一半
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.69,0:05:32.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對!把我們兄弟的格言,說來看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.08,0:05:37.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼也分開,什麼也分開 …You are
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.59,0:05:41.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,心情很好的一半布其兄弟啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.27,0:05:44.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這是露易·麻煩大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.06,0:05:48.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哥哥,不是"麻煩" ,不是"威嚇"嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.36,0:05:52.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蠢材啊!起碼也要記得自己波士的名字嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.55,0:05:56.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我是這第一星界的波士 露易·瑪格西 大人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.70,0:06:03.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一半布其兄弟,看看這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.11,0:06:06.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.59,0:06:09.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,反抗多壞達大人的愚蠢的家夥渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.17,0:06:10.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.03,0:06:15.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,明白嗎?找出這個渡,消滅他!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.70,0:06:16.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.45,0:06:25.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,以前的喜傑鎮,是個非常和平的市鎮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.20,0:06:26.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.24,0:06:54.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一半布其兄弟來到這個鎮後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.58,0:06:58.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,把所有東西用牆壁分開了一半
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.49,0:07:03.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,令電影也只能看到一半
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.77,0:07:06.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,巴士在中間分開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.69,0:07:10.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,網球也變成了小孩子的羽毛球了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.73,0:07:18.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不單這樣,整個市鎮也被那道牆分開了一半
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.90,0:07:22.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那麼雖然是同一個鎮,但是那邊也不能過來這邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.64,0:07:25.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這邊也不能過去那邊嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.41,0:07:30.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是,我的未婚妻,是在牆的另一邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.55,0:07:32.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是過分的事呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.15,0:07:37.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的令人非常生氣,不能饒恕!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.25,0:07:39.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可惡的一半布其兄弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.70,0:07:47.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真不知道什麼叫做隔牆有耳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.73,0:07:50.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡他們沒有發現呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.78,0:07:54.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一定會嚇他們一跳,這真好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.05,0:07:58.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼也分開,什麼也分開…GO!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.75,0:08:03.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡,有些牆飛來了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.92,0:08:12.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很厲害!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.52,0:08:13.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家沒事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.77,0:08:16.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒問題!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.37,0:08:17.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,咦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.46,0:08:20.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個侍應哥哥呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.13,0:08:21.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我在這邊啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.27,0:08:27.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡,已不能再忍下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.24,0:08:33.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯!師傅、火美子\N走吧!把一半布其兄弟打到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.26,0:08:46.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在和渡打之前要先填飽了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.33,0:08:50.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一人一半的菜,什麼時候也這麼好吃呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.23,0:08:57.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要你們久等了,今天的主菜是竹莢魚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.64,0:09:02.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,已很友好地分開一半了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.37,0:09:04.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,竹莢魚…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.95,0:09:09.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,呀?這個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.65,0:09:13.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什…什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.72,0:09:17.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你那邊不是有魚尾嗎?你也是有魚頭啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.95,0:09:22.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以…這樣不是一人一半啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.32,0:09:30.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.07,0:09:36.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這便是分隔開的牆呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.33,0:09:41.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真厲害呢,到底延伸到哪裏呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.83,0:09:43.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我去看一看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.49,0:09:50.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,忍法,行牆之術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.50,0:09:58.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,厲害…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.11,0:10:10.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,去…去到哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.44,0:10:15.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡,找到牆的盡頭了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.90,0:10:16.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.00,0:10:19.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有啊,有啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.91,0:10:21.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那麼在哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.54,0:10:27.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,越過30個山,河也渡過20條河後便有了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.19,0:10:30.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,去不了那麼遠的地方啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.33,0:10:36.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看來只能爬過去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.87,0:10:39.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我來了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.41,0:10:42.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,師傅!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.20,0:10:48.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,變成河馬燒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.58,0:10:49.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,河馬燒,河馬燒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.64,0:10:53.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為什麼火美子會沒事的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.48,0:10:56.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到底怎樣做才好?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.96,0:11:06.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很久沒試過地燃燒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.39,0:11:09.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那麼我們去吧,弟弟!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.09,0:11:15.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡的人頭,讓我們分開他一半吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.12,0:11:31.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎樣才能越過這道牆呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.09,0:11:34.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,火美子,你靜一點啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.85,0:11:36.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我和師傅正在想辦法啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.08,0:11:39.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,用我的忍法便簡單了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.77,0:11:40.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.83,0:11:43.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,交給我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.76,0:11:49.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,忍法,大家一起玩翹翹板
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.84,0:11:56.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你們坐在那裏吧,這邊嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.98,0:12:01.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那會變成怎樣?有點不安的感覺呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.35,0:12:06.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡,我來了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.53,0:12:14.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大成功啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.81,0:12:17.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,火美子,怎樣著陸啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.80,0:12:18.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.55,0:12:19.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎會的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.95,0:12:35.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,鐵皮兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.94,0:12:41.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真蠢,他們是比鐵皮兵更強的鋼鐵兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.26,0:12:44.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你們就是一半布其兄弟嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.35,0:12:51.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對,我們就是第一星界中最有合作性的一半布其兄弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.39,0:12:54.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,上吧,鋼鐵兵!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.14,0:12:55.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,危險!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.37,0:13:03.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,伏擊人實在太卑鄙了,讓我劍部武一郎來解決你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.67,0:13:13.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.66,0:13:18.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,讓我們告訴電視機前面的各位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.10,0:13:25.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡胸口的三角形是一種叫\N回轉龍圓盤的必殺特別道具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.58,0:13:26.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這個回轉龍圓盤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.24,0:13:29.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是渡帶到創界山的飛碟遊戲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.88,0:13:33.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,由聖龍妃大人把它變成武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.60,0:13:34.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家還記得嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.48,0:13:37.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那麼請繼續觀賞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.33,0:13:39.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對了,還有這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.78,0:13:44.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是回轉龍圓盤還真繞口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.54,0:13:46.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒有更好的名字嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.80,0:13:50.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小渡,可不可以不要在這時候想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.36,0:13:55.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是沒有一個好名字就很難出招呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.49,0:14:01.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,飄…飄…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.55,0:14:03.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,屁股在飄呀飄呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.60,0:14:06.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,飄飄?對了,是飄飄了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.62,0:14:07.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是飄飄了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.81,0:14:11.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,飄飄攻擊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.72,0:14:25.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好有型,這個很有效呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.19,0:14:29.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我在這邊啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.91,0:14:33.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,野牛武一郎流,交叉字斬!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.55,0:14:40.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看啊,這就是我的必殺技了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.56,0:14:48.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,野牛武一郎流,千刀斬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.62,0:14:54.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,微塵斬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.50,0:14:57.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,方塊斬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.27,0:15:01.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不管是從何處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.93,0:15:02.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,隨便攻過來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.86,0:15:03.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,攻過來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.00,0:15:08.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,混帳,不要小看我們很和好的兄弟啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.80,0:15:10.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,上吧,哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.09,0:15:14.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼也分開 什麼也分開… GO!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.78,0:15:32.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,糟了,星龍劍被…\N這樣不能叫龍神丸出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.75,0:15:33.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.03,0:15:37.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,讓你分成兩邊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.72,0:15:42.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好,這樣的話…神奇飯團!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.46,0:15:49.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.31,0:15:51.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這盒是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.21,0:15:54.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊!好像很好吃的飯團呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.16,0:15:57.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,師傅,把我擲到牆的後面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.27,0:15:58.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.04,0:16:00.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒事的,快點吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.13,0:16:04.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,準備…去!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.75,0:16:08.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不夠高
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.09,0:16:15.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,龍神丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.57,0:16:49.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼也分開,華奇倫!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.10,0:17:04.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,駕駛室也是和好的一人一半
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.72,0:17:06.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,牆壁飛彈發射!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.74,0:17:11.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,龍神丸,去吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.40,0:17:13.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,龍雷拳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.46,0:17:26.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他射出的牆可以攻擊,也可以防衛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.78,0:17:27.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要大意!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.64,0:17:30.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我知道了,這樣的話從空中攻擊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.68,0:17:32.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,飛吧,龍神丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.49,0:17:39.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,電話在哪裏呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.54,0:17:46.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎會這樣?\N總之把卡插進去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.67,0:17:52.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,戰-神,這邊是丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.84,0:17:53.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,然後是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.85,0:17:56.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是麻煩呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.66,0:18:08.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,從後攻擊吧,龍神丸,加速!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.44,0:18:13.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蠢材,蠢材
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.54,0:18:23.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這是華奇倫的一半攻擊啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.38,0:18:26.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再試一次吧,龍神丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.28,0:18:40.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,從你的頭頂開始斬開你一半
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.36,0:18:42.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等一等,等一等!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.70,0:18:53.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,打得好…大叔打得好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.06,0:18:54.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,交給在下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.93,0:18:57.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,上吧上吧…渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.47,0:19:14.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一半飛彈的威力怎樣啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.11,0:19:16.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,勝負已分了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.83,0:19:20.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哥哥,用剛才的飯團慶祝吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.56,0:19:22.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好,和好的一人一半吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.74,0:19:31.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼了?你的比較重耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.68,0:19:35.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼可能,飯團分得很平均啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.68,0:19:36.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那讓我看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.12,0:19:38.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我的是這樣!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.45,0:19:40.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我的也一樣!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.25,0:19:42.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.55,0:19:45.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.69,0:19:51.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你…你的飯團…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.49,0:19:54.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,酸梅…有酸梅啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.97,0:19:58.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,誰知道啊,我分得很均衡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.76,0:20:03.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是什麼聲音啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.74,0:20:06.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可惡,對自己太偏心了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.84,0:20:08.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我討厭"一半"了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.19,0:20:11.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我真正喜歡的名言是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.14,0:20:12.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一個人獨佔!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.23,0:20:16.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我還不是一樣討厭"一半"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.46,0:20:17.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,欠揍嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.25,0:20:18.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這家夥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.42,0:20:25.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎…怎麼了?他們…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.92,0:20:29.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看來好像感情決裂了,是機會了,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.73,0:20:30.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.86,0:20:38.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,必殺!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.45,0:20:42.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,星龍劍!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.01,0:20:57.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,斬得不夠正中啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.65,0:21:18.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的很多謝你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.91,0:21:22.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,全靠你們我才能這樣和未婚妻相見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.41,0:21:26.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你們是在找星之風的起風處吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.06,0:21:28.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你知道些什麼嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.43,0:21:33.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是,吹出星之風的地方\N在一座美麗的城堡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.04,0:21:38.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我在小時候,從婆婆的口中聽到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.58,0:21:40.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,美麗的城堡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.64,0:21:44.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,星之風宮殿\N婆婆是這樣說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.25,0:21:47.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,星之風宮殿嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.45,0:21:52.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡,看來我們已清楚目的地了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.58,0:21:54.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡,Let's go!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.37,0:21:55.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.82,0:22:18.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好,目的地是星之風宮殿!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.10,0:22:33.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼了?這個胸口在驅跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.17,0:22:35.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蹦蹦在跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.77,0:22:39.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Stop!已不能停止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.66,0:22:44.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,連你也一個勁兒地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.51,0:22:48.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,油門不用放開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.76,0:22:52.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一直踏著 Go!Go!Go!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.88,0:22:56.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,流星也不能代替
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.92,0:23:01.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因為是速度的戀愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.16,0:23:04.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,TONIGHT
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:04.86,0:23:08.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,秘密的旋律笨拙的舞蹈 Dancin'
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.91,0:23:12.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,能夠抱到她的心 LUCKY
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.01,0:23:17.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一直望著的瞳孔湧上了 HAPPY
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.23,0:23:20.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你是 MY GIRL
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.45,0:23:24.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今夜 MY LOVE
